::Shredder/Ramulus/Mosquitor::

Shredder apears in the forest, instantly setting off toward the 
destron base.

"I'm back," he says over his comm-link to all destrons, "What'd I 
miss?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus runs back toward the Ark, hearing gunfire coming from it.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Mosquitor flies up to Hell Beast.

"How may I serve you, leadership," he asks mindlessly, waiting for a 
responce.
